.DT
set_gender
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_gender

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_gender -  This method sets the gender of the deity.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_gender(string deity,
int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the deity name
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the gender to set the deity to

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the gender of the deity.  The gender is the same
as used elsehwere in the game.  0 for neuter, 1 for male and 2 for female.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/std/living/gender.c
.EP

